{
  "type": "doc",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "First: What Is a Server and Why Do We Talk to It?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "A "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "server"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is just another computer whose job is to:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Receive requests"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Process them"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Send responses back"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "When you:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Open a website"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Fetch data from an API"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Submit a form"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "You’re talking to a server."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Most of the time, your "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "browser"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " does this for you."
        },
        {
          "type": "hardBreak"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "But developers often need to talk to servers "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "directly"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "—without a UI."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "That’s where cURL enters the chat."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "What is cURL? (Very Simple Explanation)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "cURL"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is a command-line tool that lets you "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "send requests to a server"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " and "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "see the response"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "That’s it. No magic."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Think of cURL as:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "“A browser without buttons, running in your terminal.”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "You tell cURL:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Where to send the request"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "What kind of request it is"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "And it shows you "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "exactly"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " what the server replies with."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Why Programmers Need cURL"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Developers use cURL because it’s:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Fast"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Scriptable"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "UI-independent"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Honest (no hidden behavior)"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "You use cURL when:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Testing APIs"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Debugging backend issues"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Checking server responses"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Verifying headers and status codes"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Working on servers with no browser"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "If you do backend, DevOps, or API work—cURL is unavoidable."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Making Your First Request Using cURL"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Let’s start with the simplest possible thing."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "curl https://example.com\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "What just happened?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "cURL sent a "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "GET request"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The server sent back a response"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "cURL printed it in your terminal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "No flags. No complexity."
        },
        {
          "type": "hardBreak"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "You just talked to a server."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "That confidence boost matters."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Understanding Request and Response"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Every interaction with a server follows the same pattern."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "src": "https://www.twilio.com/content/dam/twilio-com/global/en/blog/legacy/2022/http-methods-requests-curl/HTTP_Request_Flow_1.png",
        "alt": "Image",
        "title": null,
        "width": null,
        "height": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "src": "https://qscxtzelbdglvzofrnvz.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/blog-images/uploads/c42a1a5e-cbf4-464d-9919-af1a903ce62f.png",
        "alt": null,
        "title": null,
        "width": null,
        "height": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The Request"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Sent by you (client):"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "URL"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Method (GET or POST)"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Optional data"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The Response"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Sent by the server:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Status code (success or failure)"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Data (HTML, JSON, text)"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Example mental model:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "“Ask → Process → Answer”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Browser Request vs cURL Request"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "src": "https://qscxtzelbdglvzofrnvz.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/blog-images/uploads/b4ef37a6-6f71-4751-9958-3c4ded8ca72c.png",
        "alt": null,
        "title": null,
        "width": null,
        "height": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "BrowsercURLHides complexityShows everythingAuto-rendersRaw responseUI-basedTerminal-basedGreat for usersGreat for developers"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "cURL doesn’t decorate."
        },
        {
          "type": "hardBreak"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "It tells the truth."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Using cURL to Talk to APIs"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "APIs are just servers expecting structured requests."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "GET Request (Read Data)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "curl https://api.example.com/users\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "This asks:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "“Give me users.”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "You’ll usually get JSON back."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 3
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "POST Request (Send Data)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "bash"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "curl -X POST https://api.example.com/users\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "This tells the server:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "“I want to create something.”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "We’re keeping it light on flags for now—confidence first, depth later."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Basic HTTP Request & Response Structure"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "src": "https://qscxtzelbdglvzofrnvz.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/blog-images/uploads/c722d0af-0800-4586-ae38-e21d50c2914e.png",
